{"tid":445121,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] Kitkat日本限定口味食評 (蘋果/士多啤梨芝士蛋糕/焦糖布甸)","createTime":"2017-10-23T05:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T08:02:28.000Z","uid":43041,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b61fbda9dc2960ce94870e5c45ee58ee4b76b562","tid":445121,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"話說係樂天買左d想食好耐既日本限定KitKat<br />\n之前食過日本茶味 同 馬來西亞三色拉茶味KitKat，兩款都一試難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（唔係綠茶）<br />\n於是對其他奇怪味既Kitkat產生興趣<br />\n<br />\n揀左幾款香港唔常見既口味<br />\n包括蘋果 焦糖布甸 士多啤梨芝士蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同日本酒味<br />\n事不宜遲開箱先<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/dmpeam/DSC_1799.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fdmpeam%2FDSC_1799.jpg&h=b7a931fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/dmpeam/DSC_1799.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fdmpeam%2FDSC_1799.jpg&h=b7a931fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一款食 信州地區限定蘋果味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/131253_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F131253_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=02b339fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/jdR31R/DSC_1804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FjdR31R%2FDSC_1804.jpg&h=78647108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/m3iST6/DSC_1803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fm3iST6%2FDSC_1803.jpg&h=6182bc08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包裝好靚，直頭好似禮盒咁<br />\n可惜上面d字睇唔明，估計係話佢地既蘋果好新鮮好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/ejSAgR/DSC_1813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FejSAgR%2FDSC_1813.jpg&h=99c074de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一打開<br />\n陣蘋果味撲面而來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一d都無誇張<br />\n食落去同平時飲開既蘋果汁味道差唔多<br />\n不過蘋果味再強烈好多，同埋無左個種甜到仆街既感覺<br />\n加落朱古力度個味道都幾夾<br />\n係衰在件朱古力溶溶地口感差小小<br />\n除左依點我覺得整體唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 值得一試<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二款食 焦糖布甸味<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/fgaSBR/Fotor_150873632239925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FfgaSBR%2FFotor_150873632239925.jpg&h=383d509c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/nrBsvm/DSC_1820.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FnrBsvm%2FDSC_1820.jpg&h=3abd7605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個包裝據說係今個萬聖節限定款<br />\n雖然比起頭先蘋果個款無咁華麗<br />\n但獨立包裝上既公仔有唔同款<br />\n可愛得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背後亦有位比你寫野 好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽其他巴打講香港759有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我唔見樓下個間有所以唔肯定，亦唔知道同可以放入焗爐個款係咪一樣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/f307T6/DSC_1821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Ff307T6%2FDSC_1821.jpg&h=220c69aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/h49eam/DSC_1825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fh49eam%2FDSC_1825.jpg&h=bed3ccf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食落去第一野有濃烈既焦糖味<br />\n我條仔形容聞落似麥當勞早餐d熱香餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後咬多幾啖就食到有奶味<br />\n而且都幾似雞蛋布甸應有既濃烈同creamy既口感<br />\n雖然價錢平過蘋果味個隻<br />\n但我比較鍾意依款 會再購買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三款係 富士山士多啤梨芝士蛋糕味<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/iZMgo6/DSC_1844.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FiZMgo6%2FDSC_1844.jpg&h=b586f934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個名好伏 我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依款既包裝最特別<br />\n應該係富士山既設計黎<br />\n上面仲寫住世界遺產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/dhwW5m/DSC_1828.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FdhwW5m%2FDSC_1828.jpg&h=bace6512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/j9HFWR/DSC_1831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fj9HFWR%2FDSC_1831.jpg&h=06fdc1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抱住會中伏既心態咬左啖<br />\n&hellip;其實唔難食<br />\n係有陣好香好清新既果味 但我唔多覺似士多啤梨味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落去完全無說好的芝士蛋糕味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而吞左之後個喉嚨涼涼地<br />\n唔知有無薄荷成份呢？<br />\n雖然比想象中好唔同<br />\n但稱唔上中伏 因為味道唔錯<br />\n對平時食開水果味零食既人黎講應該幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後日本酒味&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我未開黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依一隻味應該大撚把人食過<br />\n不過轉左新包裝，唔知味道有無變<br />\n等個post有人睇先算<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打有咩奇怪味既KitKat推薦？提議下我下次買邊隻味好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9541ce34fd2014608a31240fd2ad6bd8632a57e1","tid":445121,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbeae6fbe8ac33e89ce721593291db6214c9e30c","tid":445121,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"果段日文都係打下飛機話佢D蘋果好靚呀 D水好清 個天好靚既環境下出既蘋果 好撚夾朱古力呀咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c648bd1e629d75a5fc2a6046dbf53b08f27fdbce","tid":445121,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"蘋果嗰盒雪凍好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}